name":"Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure – Tile Tower","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"thing","objectid":"318457","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgameaccessory/318457/overboss-a-boss-monster-adventure-tile-tower","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgameaccessory/318457/overboss-a-boss-monster-adventure-tile-tower"}],"cardset":[{"name":null,"sortindex":null,"objecttype":"family","objectid":"91379","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/cardset/91379/","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/cardset/91379/"}]},"linkcounts":{"boardgamedesigner":2,"boardgamesolodesigner":0,"boardgameartist":2,"boardgamepublisher":3,"boardgamedeveloper":0,"boardgamegraphicdesigner":1,"boardgamesculptor":0,"boardgameeditor":0,"boardgamewriter":0,"boardgameinsertdesigner":2,"boardgamehonor":0,"boardgamecategory":3,"boardgamemechanic":6,"boardgameexpansion":2,"boardgameversion":3,"expandsboardgame":0,"boardgameintegration":1,"contains":0,"containedin":0,"reimplementation":0,"reimplements":0,"boardgamefamily":4,"videogamebg":1,"boardgamesubdomain":1,"boardgameaccessory":2,"cardset":1},"secondarynamescount":0,"alternatenamescount":2,"primaryname":{"nameid":"1799936","name":"Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure"},"alternatenames":[{"nameid":"2203940","name":"Overboss: Gra w świecie Boss Monstera"},{"nameid":"2205939","name":"Overboss: Votre monde en 16 bit"}],"description":"<p>In <em><strong>Overboss</strong></em>, rival Boss Monsters emerge from their dungeons to conquer the Overworld. Each turn, players draft and place terrain tiles and monster tokens. Their goal: to craft the map with the greatest Power and become the ultimate Overboss!</p>\n\n<p>Designed by Aaron Mesburne and Kevin Russ (<em>Calico</em>), this fast-paced game combines drafting, set collection, and puzzly tile laying. It's set in the retro-inspired pixel art world of Brotherwise Games' best-selling <em>Boss Monster</em>, but this is an entirely new experience.</p>\n\n<p>Build your map by drafting Forests, Swamps, Caves, Camps, Graveyards, Dungeon Entrances and other landscapes. Each terrain type has a different point value, and some increase in Power as you acquire larger sets. Players must balance optimal placement, set values, and disrupt their opponents' sets. You'll also need to manage monsters, which award points when grouped together or placed on matching terrain.</p>\n\n<p>The game includes everything needed for up to 5 players: over 120 terrain tiles, over 100 monster tokens, 5 double-sided player boards, a scorepad, and more.</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher (updated for added content)</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong><a class=\"\" href=\"/wiki/page/Microbadges#\">Microbadges</a>:</strong>  <a href=\"/microbadge/50372\"><img alt='Microbadge: Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_50372_0.png\"></a> <a href=\"/microbadge/50373\"><img alt='Microbadge: Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Overboss: A Boss Monster Adventure', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_50373_0.png\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.brotherwisegames.com/s/Overboss-FAQ-v8.pdf\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '_blank'); return false;\">Official FAQ</a></p>\n\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.brotherwisegames.com/s/Overboss-Printable-Score-Sheets.pdf\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '_blank'); return false;\">Extra Scoresheets</a></p>\n\n","website":{"url":"https://www.brotherwisegames.com/overboss","title":"\"Overboss\" official English page"},"imageid":"5650097","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/t8tLdsAhe5e9tmel47BtmQ__small/img/1m